longBusinessSummary: Golden Wheel Tiandi Holdings Company Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development of commercial and residential properties in Mainland China and Hong Kong. The company operates through three segments: Property Development, Property Leasing, and Hotel Operation. It develops and sells properties; and offers property leasing services, including the lease of self-owned properties and sub-lease of rented properties, as well as operates hotels. The company also develops and operates shopping malls; and provides property decoration services. Golden Wheel Tiandi Holdings Company Limited was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Nanjing, China.
